Heading1.Text: Energy Entrepreneurs Fund 9: questions and answers

Body1.Text: Questions asked ahead of the session will be answered at the applicant information presentation on 12 November 2021. All answers will also be published after the event.

Body2.Text: To submit your questions please email general.entrepreneur@BEIS.gov.uk

Body3.Text: You can also review answers from previous rounds of the fund here.

Body4.Text: To register to attend the event email general.entrepreneur@beis.gov.uk with the subject line, Event registration and we will send you the details.
